The paper discusses a multi-robotic system algorithm for cleaning an environment, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of path planning algorithm and efficiency in cleaning suggest the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of iRobot Creates, which are mobile robots, indicating the involvement of machine learning (cs.MA) and computer vision (cs.CV) in the system.
